Brazil bought 75,000 tonnes ofFrench wheat at tonight's tender, a Brazilian Wheat Boardspokesman said.    For May shipment, it accepted offers from J. Souflet for50,000 tonnes of wheat at 83.49 dlrs Fob per tonne.    For June shipment, Brazil bought 25,000 tonnes from J.Souflet also at 83.49 dlrs Fob per tonne.    The next tender is set for April 9, for May, June and Julyshipment, the spokesman said. Reuter&#3;